    {
      "note": "description",
      "abstract": "Requires and appropriates funds for the Department of Transportation to establish a pilot program to offer fully subsidized public transit passes for department employees.  Requires a report to the Legislature.  Effective 7/1/3000.  (HD1)"
    }
